title: Metal sheets bending machine- US-WS-1.5*1300 mm

short_description: This US-WS-1.5*1300 mm equipment serves for manual bending of metal sheets. The equipment can be bent up to 60°. It can bend sheets with a thickness of 0.3 mm to 1.5 mm and a length of up to 1300 mm. The equipment weighs 360 kg, its dimensions are: length 1980 mm, width 800 mm and height 1320 mm. Other models of this equipment are shown below, and they differ from each other in terms of price and parameters.
short_description_uz: Ushbu US-WS-1.5*1300 mm uskuna metal listlarni qo'lda (ruchnoy) bukish uchun xizmat qiladi. Uskuna 60° gacha bukish imkoniyatiga ega. Bukish qalinligi 0.3 mm dan 1.5 mm gacha bo'lgan, hamda uzunligi 1300 mm gacha bo'lgan listlarni buka oladi. Uskuna 360 kg vaznga ega, o'lchamlari: uzunligi 1980 mm, kengligi 800 mm va balandligi 1320 mm dan iborat. Quyida ushbu uskunaning boshqa modellari ham aks etgan va ular narx, hamda parametrlarda bir-biridan farqlanadi.
